        <prompt>How did the "Great Upheaval" of 1877 change American labor relations?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Demonstrated the power of organized labor strikes</option>
            <option letter="b">Led to immediate worker benefits</option>
            <option letter="c">Created new labor laws</option>
            <option letter="d">Unified all workers permanently</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
