    <question number="34">
        <prompt>What was the significance of the "Molly Maguires"?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Secret labor organization in Pennsylvania coal fields</option>
            <option letter="b">Railroad workers union</option>
            <option letter="c">Women's rights group</option>
            <option letter="d">Political reform movement</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The Molly Maguires were a secret organization of Irish coal miners who used violence to protest working conditions, leading to controversial trials and executions.</explanation>
